Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:03.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:10.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Today's ****** was ******* because \Nof the ******* *************,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so we have a ****** ******** \Nspecial that's basically a *****!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:51.00,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing Lasts Forever, Including Parents, Money, \NYouth, Your Room, Dress Shirts, Me, You, and the Gintama Anime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.98,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.25,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea what you said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.76,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,at the beginning because of all the censoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Read between the lines, Pachi-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at what we're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And a kotatsu in May?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:05.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They're reusing old footage \Nfor this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Eight episodes into the new show and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we're already resorting to cheap tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And eight's supposed to be a lucky number?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:11.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder your name has \NJapanese word for eight in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:13.11,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.00,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The success of the movie led to the \NTV series returning after one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.88,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was going too smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.74,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,This show is always on the \Nverge of falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.53,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The second series could end at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.61,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,We might as well air the same episode \Neight times, starting next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:26.91,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Since Shinpachi's name has \Nthe word for eight in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.79,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.04,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And first, we have to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,what we're doing for the rest of this episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.57,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep reusing old footage \Nwhile babbling about nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.82,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,the producers who were \Nso happy about the show
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:40.26,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,coming back will have to go back to apologizing to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's play a song for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A song for the valiant efforts \Nof Hasegawa-san, who's managed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.89,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to survive despite his dark future, much like this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:59.19,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:06:12.93,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,"The God of Cardboard"\NMADAO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:07.29,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.75,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.56,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,My home, my job, my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.30,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't fight back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.26,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,as I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.43,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,And then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.77,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,became a middle-aged dumb-ass oldie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.56,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken everything away,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.19,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,but the God of Cardboard gives stuff to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:42.24,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard can be transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.20,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,into a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.04,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,At night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.96,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,cardboard keeps away the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:04:01.09,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:08.06,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,O, God of Cardboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:15.35,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:23.07,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I softly closed my eyes and went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.55,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.01,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,My pride, my savings, my assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:51.06,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't fight back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.02,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,as I wore down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.77,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,And then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:01.61,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Was still a middle-aged dumb-ass oldie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.41,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:10.37,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,But the God of Cardboard gives stuff to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.95,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard can be transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.92,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,into a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:24.92,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard keeps away prying eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:32.81,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:39.86,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,O, God of Cardboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:47.24,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:54.75,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I softly curled up into a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:11.64,Main01,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cardboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.62,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly benefited from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.98,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,750)}Special Announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:29.45,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}The Gintama Movie Production Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.52,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.40,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of falling into enemy hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.95,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,we should finish this like warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.86,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,and cut open our bellies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:36.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to plan out a pretty death,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:40.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,why not live a pretty life to the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Zura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.32,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Zura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.20,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:57.72,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,The man's silver hair was lined with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:07.50,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,He tore across the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.30,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,...like a Yaksha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.97,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Gintama the Movie II
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:19.22,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Birth of the White Yaksha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.22,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.13,Main01,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,This blessed land
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.55,Main01,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,should not be wasted on those barbaric apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.78,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.70,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Kiheitai! Follow my lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.98,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You just charged in by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.59,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You crazy in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.51,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.67,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.20,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.43,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Need a hand, Gintoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.47,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.04,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:20.54,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,This war is killing off my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.96,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.29,Main01,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,...watching friends die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.23,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.82,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.08,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.17,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.95,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:29.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shoyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:32.40,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}This is when it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:37.19,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Coming next spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:42.16,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Also screening:\NShinsengumi\N- Arrival in Kyoto -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:50.42,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Preorder Bonus\NEveryone who preorders their tickets will receive Elizabeth 3D glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.68,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I didn't expect the second movie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.78,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to cover this storyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They're following up the success of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:02.84,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Gintama the Movie: Benizakura Arc the New Translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And this isn't a rehash of one \Nof the arcs from the TV series.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is a completely original story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.60,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,No one thought that the fake movie scam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,from Jump Anime Tour 2008 would become real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-ups are scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They're quick as lightning to ride on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.69,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the coattails of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Fastest in the world, or so they claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.13,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we can do a movie every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:27.31,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,If this one is an original story,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.73,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the next one can be another remake of a TV arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.51,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,After "Birth of the White Yaksha,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.51,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we can do "Kagura and the Steel Troops."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That arc doesn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.96,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And you clearly copied that \Ntitle from someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:41.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm pretty sure that the \Naudience has noticed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.06,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Noticed what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're sitting here talking \Nabout a second movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...but it ain't gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:54.65,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Life ain't easy for this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.12,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.81,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying through your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We had a successful movie run \Nand the series is back on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.91,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and you're still trying to pull that crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.70,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The successful movie only made \N1/4 of what One Piece did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The success of Gintama the Movie: \NBenizakura Arc the New Translation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,was somewhat because we spent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:24.29,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,four years lying about making a movie on the TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't big daddies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't plant our seed on an annual basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.40,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of metaphor is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:32.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll need to spend time \Nsetting up the next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,In three years, when the next World Cup is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.68,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Though this show might not make
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.19,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,it past the preliminaries for movie consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.53,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't even trying, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.98,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:52.58,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, the second movie \Nwon't use this storyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.70,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Okita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.82,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Birth of the White Yaksha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:13:01.34,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinsengumi will look even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.12,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.89,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,So if there's a second movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.95,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,it should be "Gintama the Movie: Okita Becomes a Sadist,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata Dies in the Wasteland."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.29,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of subtitle is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.01,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you kind of copying \Nthe title from someone else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.48,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you killing me off?!
