Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.14,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a go at being the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.62,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Then the three of us can be the \Nmain characters of the next movie,
