Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:53.59,Main01,Elizabeth,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're One Piece Quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.70,Main01,Elizabeth,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it took four years \Nto make 1/4 the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.11,Main01,Elizabeth,0000,0000,0000,,So if you want to be number one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.84,Main01,Elizabeth,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to spend sixteen years preparing.
