Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.72,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do we do, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:20.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it.
