Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.66,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,One Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Mr. Ginpachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:58.10,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:03.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go straight to the first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,From someone with the pen name YNG:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,In episode 197, "Not Losing to the Storm",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,there was a scene where \NGin-san was hit in the balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:17.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl, so I don't \Nknow how much that hurts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but a certain person said that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.38,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,"it hurts as much as a direct ignore-defense attack
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,on the abdominal area after a body blow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:27.84,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,removed all of the abs and other protection down there."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:33.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me a simple \Nexplanation of how much it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This question has been \Nkeeping me up at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Abdominal area without \Nany abs makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have abs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but no balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:51.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use a metaphor that's more romantic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.70,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so the girls will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:54.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:17:00.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,that you are drinking tea \Nin a field of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:04.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And then your pet bunny escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:08.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You run after it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but a prince on a white \Nhorse happens to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:14.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,However, he doesn't have \Nenough time to react,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and the white horse stomps on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:20.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,However, you were wearing \Na helmet, so you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:25.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But then the prince loses his \Nbalance and is thrown off the horse
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:28.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and is about to hit the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,when your butler catches him in mid-air
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,since your butler used to be a gymnast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But since your butler strained \Nhimself, his back gives,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,leaving him in excruciating pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Your butler screams in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But then he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:47.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was all his dream
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:51.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,in a crappy book that left you in pain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and your mother in more \Npain as she watches you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and your father in even more pain \Nafter he accidentally hit his balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:05.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,After a long suspension, he's finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:11.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, bringing chaos and \Ndestruction back to class 3-Z...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.44,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I simply destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.92,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Heartless and hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.60,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Takasugi-kun!
