Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Close your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Mr. Kakashi from class N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.83,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,had his Sharingan stolen after school yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a few suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but it's too much effort so I'm going \Nto pick someone from this classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.72,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Teach! Takasugi-kun looks suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.18,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,He must be hiding the Sharingan \Nunder that eye patch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.61,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to copy my Ninja Centerfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Takasugi?
