Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:05.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand why the delinquent \NTakasugi would be a suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:09.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but he doesn't need the Sharingan \Nto improve his image.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Takasugi already has \Nplenty of emo kiddie tendencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,such as being a delinquent, \Nwearing an eye patch,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.36,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and having a desire to destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.76,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to destroy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I recommend that you refrain \Nfrom picking up new personality traits
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,to boost your popularity \Nin the character rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:32.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only confuse the audience \Nby adding to your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:35.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,New additions frequently fail hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It happens all the time in anime sequels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:38.91,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.80,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Those characters tend to be written off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.55,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.80,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Teach, I feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.56,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.91,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Shimura.
