Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:41.04,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,To turn the Kabuki District \Ninto a garden of bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:44.36,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason for us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:47.55,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Four factions -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:48.05,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,After all, isn't our enemy Jirocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.60,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,350)}In an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.85,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards ready to have \Nyour balls ripped out?!
