Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:00.19,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}drops in unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:01.36,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can take \Nmy balls by teaming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.19,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any members in my faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:08.61,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Emotions intertwine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:09.85,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,They serve no use at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:08.86,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of waiting for you to pay the rent. Take your fools and scram. Never come back to this town.\N-Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:11.49,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,They just happen to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.24,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,...my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:17.65,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the White Yaksha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:20.92,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,1)}Two warriors who refuse to back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:20.92,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty more like you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:26.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Crush us if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:28.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The Otose Family will
